{"id":117292,"date":[{"year":1946,"month":10,"day":18}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"读者的话","column":"","genre":"","count":"92","ytitle":"","mtitle":"和“秋感”","ftitle":"","authors":["山翁"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山翁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬和三壶居士秋感原韻一首井乞诸　呤侣赐和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"词客哀时复感秋，相煎箕豆未曾休。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若同傀儡惭无地，倘是英雄上有楼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八载干戈民已困，千年本脈国须谋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从来樽俎消乖戾，谈笑何如定九州!"}]}